== Etymology ==
*Someone who makes a fool of himself on the [[Internet]] (mainly on [[IRC]]).

==Origins==
'''Llamah''' is a term derived from [[lamer]] after the later evolved through use in the internet. Llamahs are a subgroup of lamers. A lamer need not be a llamah.
Llamahs are usually pictured as [[Llama]]s

